item.title: LeetCode 204. Count Primes
item.description: 简单介绍素数判断及其分布规律。 Description 题目链接 Count the number of prime numbers less than a non-negative number n. Example: 1 2 3 Input: 10 Output: 4 Explanation: There are 4 prime numbers less than 10, they are 2, 3, 5, 7. 思路分析 使用埃拉托斯特尼筛选法
